# Priority Rules

If multiple reactions apply at the same time, do not spam users.

Use this priority:

1. Game over reactions
2. Detective private reactions
3. Doctor clutch/save reactions
4. Mafia kill/fail reactions
5. Vote elimination reactions
6. Tie/abstain reactions
7. Flavor reactions

Show maximum 1 to 2 popups per event.

Do not show weaker duplicate reactions if a stronger one already applies.

Examples:

* If Doctor blocks Mafia attack, show 01 to all, 24 to target, 25 to Mafia if scoped queue supports it.
* If Doctor clutch save applies, show 20 to Doctor instead of 23.
* If village eliminates Doctor, use 26 instead of generic 17 if it was by vote.
* If village eliminates Detective, use 27 instead of generic 18 if it was by vote.
* If repeated tie applies, prefer 29 over 16.

