# Security Requirements

* Do not leak hidden roles.
* Do not show Doctor/Detective death publicly unless role reveal is enabled.
* Do not show Mafia-only reactions to non-Mafia.
* Do not show Detective result reactions to anyone except Detective.
* Do not let frontend decide private audience visibility.
* Backend should provide already-authorized reactions where possible.
* Guest users and authenticated users must both be supported.

